entries.femaleVariant: One big shithole. A goddamn crater of shit. That's Pacifica.
Eh, the Voodoos are doing their best.
Yeah, sittin' in their little hideout, playin' cat-and-mouse with Netwatch. Call that their best?
So you'd rather have corpo police running around? Me, I'm fine wi' what we got.
Least the police would pretend to keep some sorta law an' order.
'Stead, whatta we got? We got the Combat Zone. The Combat Zone! Fuckin' micropocalypse right here.
Hm, fair. Heard they been findin' bodies on the edges, eyes gouged clean out.
